QuestData.Title: The Qiraji Conqueror
QuestData.CompletionText: Never have I seen such tenacity! The Bronze Flight grants you one final enchantment. The Timeless One himself has requested it so!$B$BHand me your signet ring so that I may make the necessary adjustments.
QuestData.RewardText: Rise, Qiraji Conqueror! Rise and be recognized!
